'''王州迪'''<ref name="明報151105"/> {{post-nominals|country=CAN|PC|QC}} （{{lang|en|Jody Wilson-Raybould}}，{{bd|1971年|3月23日|||catIdx=Wilson-Raybould, Jody}}），音译名为'''乔迪·威尔逊-雷布爾德'''<ref>{{cite web |title=总理府施压“开后门”？ 加拿大前高官将作证 |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2019-02/28/c_1210069400.htm |website=新华网 |accessdate=2020-12-28 |date=2019-02-28 |archive-date=2019-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191013014252/http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2019-02/28/c_1210069400.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[加拿大|加拿大]][[夸夸嘉夸族|夸夸嘉夸族]]政治人物和律師，2015年至2021年間擔任[[加拿大國會下議院|加拿大國會下議院]]議員，代表[[溫哥華固蘭湖選區|溫哥華固蘭湖選區]]。她曾為[[加拿大自由黨|加拿大自由黨]]黨員，2015年至2019年間在[[加拿大總理|總理]][[賈斯汀·杜魯多|賈斯汀·杜魯多]][[加拿大内閣|内閣]]中先後出任[[加拿大司法部長及檢察總長|司法部長兼檢察總長]]和[[加拿大退伍军人部|退伍軍人部長]]。2019年她指控總理杜魯多干預司法後被逐出自由黨，此後以[[無黨籍|獨立]]身份在國會議政。從政前她曾任[[卑詩省|卑詩省]][[刑事檢控專員|刑事檢控專員]]、卑詩條約委員會委員及卑詩第一民族議會地區酋長。

== 早年生活及事業 ==
王州迪在溫哥華綜合醫院誕生，父親比爾·威爾遜（{{lang|en|Bill Wilson}}）為卑詩原住民政治人物<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/old-video-of-pierre-trudeau-and-bill-wilson-foreshadows-political-success-of-kids-1.3305538?cmp=rss |title=Old Video of Pierre Trudeau and Bill Wilson Foreshadows Political Success of Kids |author=Karen Larsen |publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|CBC News]] |date=2015-11-05 |accessdate=2016-02-05 |archive-date=2016-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206044513/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/old-video-of-pierre-trudeau-and-bill-wilson-foreshadows-political-success-of-kids-1.3305538?cmp=rss |dead-url=no }}</ref>，母親桑德拉（{{lang|en|Sandra Wilson}}）則為一名教師<ref name="CBC151104">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/justice-minister-jody-wilson-raybould-1.3303609 |title=B.C. MP Jody Wilson-Raybould named justice minister |publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|CBC News]] |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2016-02-05 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309005025/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/justice-minister-jody-wilson-raybould-1.3303609 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。王州迪擁有[[夸夸嘉夸族|夸夸嘉夸族]]血統，為該族旗下威懷凱族國（We Wai Kai Nation）一員，其夸夸嘉夸語名稱「Puglaas」意思為「擁有貴族血統的女人」<ref name="明報151105">{{cite news |url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20151105/vaa4_r.htm |title=三名卑詩閣員小檔案 |publisher=《[[明報|明報]]》加西版 |date=2015-11-05 |accessdate=2016-02-05 |archive-date=2016-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302051939/http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20151105/vaa4_r.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="CBC151104"/>。她童年曾居於[[溫哥華|溫哥華]]，父母離異後由母親撫養<ref>{{cite news|title=Divorce law changes close to home for justice minister|url=http://www.cbc.ca/radio/thehouse/will-ottawa-and-kinder-morgan-reach-a-deal-1.4675873/divorce-law-changes-close-to-home-for-justice-minister-1.4678028|publisher=CBC News|date=May 26, 2018|access-date=October 7, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616234623/http://www.cbc.ca/radio/thehouse/will-ottawa-and-kinder-morgan-reach-a-deal-1.4675873/divorce-law-changes-close-to-home-for-justice-minister-1.4678028|archive-date=June 16, 2018}}</ref>，並跟隨母親先後在[[溫哥華島|溫哥華島]]的{{tsl|en|Port Hardy, British Columbia|哈迪港}}和{{tsl|en|Comox, British Columbia|科莫克斯}}居住<ref>{{cite news|last=Farrell|first=Terry|date=November 4, 2015|title=Rachel Blaney represents diversity in Parliament|url=http://www.comoxvalleyrecord.com/news/340262361.html|newspaper=Comox Valley Record|access-date=February 5, 2016|quote=''Liberal MP Jody Wilson-Raybould, who won the Vancouver Granville seat, has North Island roots. She is a member of the  We Wai Kai Nation (Cape Mudge) of Quadra Island and went to middle (Robb Road) and high school (Highland) in Comox.''|archive-date=2016-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206042507/http://www.comoxvalleyrecord.com/news/340262361.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

她於[[維多利亞大學_(加拿大)|維多利亞大學]]修讀政治學和歷史，1996年獲得文學士學位<ref>{{cite web |url=https://ring.uvic.ca/news/three-uvic-alumnae-new-federal-cabinet |title=Three UVic alumnae in new federal cabinet |publisher=[[維多利亞大學_(加拿大)|維多利亞大學]] |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2016-02-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206131337/https://ring.uvic.ca/news/three-uvic-alumnae-new-federal-cabinet |archivedate=2016-02-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，後來到[[卑詩大學|卑詩大學]][[彼得·埃拉德法學院|法學院]]修讀法律並於1999年畢業<ref name="CBC151104"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.ubc.ca/2015/11/04/ubc-alumnus-justin-trudeau-sworn-in-as-canadas-23rd-prime-minister/ |title=UBC alumnus Justin Trudeau sworn in as Canada's 23rd prime minister |publisher=[[卑詩大學|卑詩大學]] |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2016-02-05 |archive-date=2018-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181008100438/http://news.ubc.ca/2015/11/04/ubc-alumnus-justin-trudeau-sworn-in-as-canadas-23rd-prime-minister/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.allard.ubc.ca/news-events/ubc-law-news/canada%E2%80%99s-newest-attorney-general |title=Canada's Newest Attorney General |publisher=[[卑詩大學|卑詩大學]]法學院 |date=2015-11-05 |accessdate=2016-02-05 |archive-date=2016-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206135738/http://www.allard.ubc.ca/news-events/ubc-law-news/canada%E2%80%99s-newest-attorney-general |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她於2000年獲得卑詩省律師資格，同年成為卑詩省檢控官<ref name="CBC151104"/>。2003年，她成為卑詩條約委員會的顧問，再於翌年獲選為該組織的其中一名委員<ref name="CBC151104"/>；該組織專責監督省政府與原住民族之間的條約談判程序。2009年，她先後當選威懷凱族國議會議員及卑詩第一民族議會地區酋長<ref name="CBC151104"/>，再於2012年連任地區酋長職位<ref>{{cite news|last1=Bramham|first1=Daphne|title=Raised to lead, Wilson-Raybould units B.C. chiefs|url=http://www.vancouversun.com/life/Daphne+Bramham+Raised+lead+Wilson+Raybould+unites+chiefs/7624509/story.html|accessdate=15 July 2015|publisher=Vancouver Sun|date=10 December 2012|archive-date=2016-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406193509/http://www.vancouversun.com/life/Daphne+Bramham+Raised+lead+Wilson+Raybould+unites+chiefs/7624509/story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

她於2008年與蒂姆·雷布爾德（{{lang|en|Tim Raybould}}）結婚<ref>{{cite news|url=http://ottawacitizen.com/news/politics/kady-jody-wilson-raybould-taking-all-steps-to-dodge-conflict-over-husbands-lobbying-gig|title=@Kady: Jody Wilson-Raybould 'taking all steps' to dodge conflict over husband's lobbying gig|newspaper=[[Ottawa_Citizen|Ottawa Citizen]]|last=O'Malley|first=Kady|access-date=October 7, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191006210948/https://ottawacitizen.com/news/politics/kady-jody-wilson-raybould-taking-all-steps-to-dodge-conflict-over-husbands-lobbying-gig|archive-date=October 6, 2019}}</ref>。

== 聯邦政壇 ==
2013年加拿大原住民發起「不再懈怠」運動（{{lang|en|Idle No More}}）以捍衛原住民權益，期間王州迪聯同國内其他原住民領袖與時任[[加拿大總理|總理]][[史提芬·哈珀|哈珀]]及其他内閣官員會面。她有感當時的[[加拿大保守黨|保守黨]]聯邦政府無視在場原住民領袖的意見，因此生了加入聯邦政壇的念頭<ref name="CTV150710">{{cite news |title=Idle No More talks influenced former chief's decision to run for Liberals |last1=Kirkup |first1=Kristy |url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/idle-no-more-talks-influenced-former-chief-s-decision-to-run-for-liberals-1.2462841 |accessdate=2016-02-05 |agency=加新社 |publisher=CTV News |date=2015-07-10 |archive-date=2015-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150712005027/http://www.ctvnews.ca/politics/idle-no-more-talks-influenced-former-chief-s-decision-to-run-for-liberals-1.2462841 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="CBC151030">{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/aboriginals-liberal-wilson-raybould-1.3296163|title=Jody Wilson-Raybould says Liberals will make 'true reconciliation' with Aboriginal Peoples|last1=Kirkup|first1=Kristy|agency=加新社|publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|CBC News]]|date=2015-10-30|accessdate=2016-02-05|archive-date=2016-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160301201440/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/aboriginals-liberal-wilson-raybould-1.3296163|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年她在[[白馬市_(加拿大)|白馬市]]出席加拿大原住民議會周年大會時與[[加拿大自由黨|自由黨]]黨魁[[賈斯汀·杜魯多|杜魯多]]碰面，在他游說下決定代表該黨參與[[2015年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2015年聯邦大選]]<ref name="CTV150710"/>。她於2014年7月在無對手競爭的情況下獲取[[溫哥華固蘭湖選區|溫哥華固蘭湖選區]]的自由黨候選人資格<ref name="CBC140731">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/jody-wilson-raybould-b-c-aboriginal-leader-to-run-for-liberals-in-vancouver-1.2724335 |title=Jody Wilson-Raybould, B.C. aboriginal leader, to run for Liberals in Vancouver |publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|CBC News]] |date=2014-07-31 |accessdate=2016-02-05 |archive-date=2016-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160301201436/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/jody-wilson-raybould-b-c-aboriginal-leader-to-run-for-liberals-in-vancouver-1.2724335 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於2015年6月離任卑詩第一民族議會地區酋長<ref>{{cite book|title=Resolution 01/2014: Transition of Regional Chief Jody Wilson-Raybould|date=9 September 2014|publisher=BCAFN 11th Annual General Meeting|accessdate=16 July 2015}}</ref>。

在2015年10月舉行的聯邦大選，王州迪以44%得票率贏取溫哥華固蘭湖選區議席，首度晉身[[加拿大國會下議院|國會下議院]]<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/liberal-mp-elect-jody-wilson-raybould-talks-aboriginal-issues-1.3282730|title = Liberal MP-elect Jody Wilson-Raybould talks aboriginal issues|last = |first = |date = 21 October 2015|work = CBC News|access-date = 22 October 2015|via = |archive-date = 2016-03-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160309075021/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/british-columbia/liberal-mp-elect-jody-wilson-raybould-talks-aboriginal-issues-1.3282730|dead-url = no}}</ref>。她於同年11月獲總理杜魯多委任為[[加拿大司法部長及檢察總長|聯邦司法部長兼檢察總長]]，成為首位原住民司法部長和第三位女性司法部長<ref name="CBC151104"/><ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/full-list-of-justin-trudeau-s-cabinet-1.3300699|title = Full list of Justin Trudeau's cabinet|last = |first = |date = 4 November 2015|work = CBC News|access-date = 4 November 2015|via = |archive-date = 2019-04-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190403163026/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/full-list-of-justin-trudeau-s-cabinet-1.3300699|dead-url = no}}</ref>，2016年1月成為[[御用大律師|御用大律師]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.pco-bcp.gc.ca/oic-ddc.asp?lang=eng&txtToDate=&txtPrecis=counsellor&Page=&txtOICID=&txtAct=&txtBillNo=&txtFromDate=&txtDepartment=&txtChapterNo=&txtChapterYear=&rdoComingIntoForce=&DoSearch=Search+%2F+List&viewattach=31704&blnDisplayFlg=1|title = Appointment of THE HONOURABLE JODY WILSON-RAYBOULD as Queen's Counsellor|date = 2016-01-26|work = [[加拿大樞密院|加拿大樞密院]]辦公室|accessdate = 2017-08-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170824223026/http://www.pco-bcp.gc.ca/oic-ddc.asp?lang=eng&txtToDate=&txtPrecis=counsellor&Page=&txtOICID=&txtAct=&txtBillNo=&txtFromDate=&txtDepartment=&txtChapterNo=&txtChapterYear=&rdoComingIntoForce=&DoSearch=Search+%2F+List&viewattach=31704&blnDisplayFlg=1|archive-date = 2017-08-24|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

=== 司法部長 ===
王州迪就任司法部長半年内在國會引入議案，就[[安樂死|安樂死]]進行立法。在時任衞生部長[[費普真|費普真]]協助下，王州迪在下議院提出C-14號法案，2016年5月31日獲下議院通過<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/assisted-dying-vote-third-reading-1.3609647|title = MPs send assisted dying bill to Senate as C-14 deadline looms|last = Zimonjic|first = Peter|date = 2016-05-31|work = CBC News|access-date = 2019-01-18|via = |archive-date = 2019-05-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190506212243/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/assisted-dying-vote-third-reading-1.3609647|dead-url = no}}</ref>，同年6月16日被上議院加入七項修正案後獲該院通過並送回下議院<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/assisted-dying-c14-senate-amendments-1.3638240|title = Assisted dying bill: Senate sends C-14 back to House with 7 amendments|last = Bryden|first = Joan|date = 2016-06-16|work = Canadian Press|access-date = 2019-01-18|via = CBC News|archive-date = 2019-02-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190213142924/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/assisted-dying-c14-senate-amendments-1.3638240|dead-url = no}}</ref>。下議院稍為修定原有法案後將之呈交上議院，並於同月17日獲該院通過並獲取[[御准|御准]]<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/assisted-dying-bill-senate-approval-1.3640195|title = Liberals' assisted-dying bill is now law after clearing final hurdles|last = Tunney|first = Catharine|date = 2016-06-17|work = CBC News|access-date = 2019-01-18|via = |archive-date = 2019-02-13|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190213135014/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/assisted-dying-bill-senate-approval-1.3640195|dead-url = no}}</ref>，在特定情況下進行安樂死自此合法。

王州迪又於2016年5月在下議院提出C-16號法案，建議修定加拿大人權法，禁止以他人的性別認同或性別表達為由而作出歧視，並修定加拿大刑法以擴充防範仇恨宣傳的保障。法案於2017年6月19日獲取御准<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.parl.ca/LegisInfo/BillDetails.aspx?Language=E&billId=8269852|title = House Government Bill C-16 (42-1)|work = [[加拿大國會|加拿大國會]]|accessdate = 2019-01-18|archive-date = 2019-02-02|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190202092317/http://www.parl.ca/LEGISINFO/BillDetails.aspx?Language=E&billId=8269852|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

[[大麻合法化|大麻合法化]]為自由黨2015年大選的政綱之一，為了落實該項政綱，王州迪於2017年4月在下議院提出C-45號法案（即大麻法）。法案於2018年6月獲國會兩院通過<ref>{{citation|title=Canada Moves One Step Closer To Marijuana Legalization – Thanks to the overwhelming support in the House of Commons, Canada moves one step closer to marijuana legalization.|author=Chloé Harper Gold|date=November 28, 2017|url=https://hightimes.com/news/canada-moves-one-step-closer-marijuana-legalization/|accessdate=2019-01-18|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612142748/https://hightimes.com/news/canada-moves-one-step-closer-marijuana-legalization/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citation|title=Canada Senate to Vote on Marijuana Legalization: Canada's Senate is expected to vote on Bill C-45, the Cannabis Act, on Thursday evening, which would make Canada the first G7 nation to legalize marijuana.|author=Tala Salem|date=June 6, 2018|publisher=US News|url=https://www.usnews.com/news/national-news/articles/2018-06-07/canada-senate-to-vote-on-marijuana-legalization|accessdate=2019-01-18|archive-date=2018-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180608014010/https://www.usnews.com/news/national-news/articles/2018-06-07/canada-senate-to-vote-on-marijuana-legalization|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{citation|title=Trudeau says pot will be legal as of Oct. 17, 2018|publisher=CBC News|date=June 20, 2018|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/cannabis-pot-legalization-bill-1.4713839|accessdate=2019-01-18|archive-date=2018-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180621014418/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/cannabis-pot-legalization-bill-1.4713839|dead-url=no}}</ref>，大麻的娛樂用途和個人種植則於同年10月17日正式合法化，加拿大遂成為全球第二個允許大麻娛樂用途的國家<ref>{{Cite news|url = https://www.cnn.com/2018/06/20/health/canada-legalizes-marijuana/index.html|title = Canada becomes second nation in the world to legalize marijuana|last = Sapra|first = Bani|date = 2018-06-20|work = CNN|access-date = 2019-01-18|via = |archive-date = 2019-02-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190212125138/https://www.cnn.com/2018/06/20/health/canada-legalizes-marijuana/index.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

=== 退伍軍人事務部長 ===
總理杜魯多於2019年1月14日重組內閣，王州迪調任退伍軍人事務部長<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/liberal-cabinet-shuffle-2019-1.4976936|title=David Lametti named Canada's new justice minister in Liberal cabinet shuffle|last=Harris|first=Kathleen|date=2019-01-14|work=CBC News|language=en|access-date=2019-01-14|archive-date=2019-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190114150437/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/liberal-cabinet-shuffle-2019-1.4976936|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但於不足一個月後請辭。

=== 國會後座 ===
{{See also|SNC－兰万灵事件|賈斯汀·杜魯多#司法干预丑闻}}

在請辭後一周，王州迪卻獲淮參與內閣會議，被指是與政府涉貪醜聞有關<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/htm/News/20190220/taa1_r.htm |title=王州迪突出席內閣會議 隨稱將赴司法委會作供 SNC-Lavalin風波發酵 反對黨抨不傳召總理辦職員 |publisher=《[[明報|明報]]》加東版 |date=2019-02-20 |accessdate=2019-12-09 |archive-date=2019-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190825092406/http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/htm/News/20190220/taa1_r.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她在2月27日於下議院司法委員會作供時指控，她任職司法部長和檢察總長期間處理著名建築公司[[SNC－蘭萬靈|SNC－蘭萬靈]]涉賄案時，受到杜魯多等人壓力，被要求取消調查，並認為她因拒絕屈服而被調任退伍軍人事務部長<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190228/mobile/bkn-20190228104608065-0228_00972_001.html|title=干預司法風波案　王州迪供稱受杜魯多不當施壓|date=2019-02-1.28|work=東方日報東網|language=zh|access-date=2019-02-28|archive-date=2019-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190301074405/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190228/mobile/bkn-20190228104608065-0228_00972_001.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/htm/News/20190228/vaa1h_r.htm |title=王州迪稱遭11人施壓 被調任皆因拒絕屈服 首次就總理涉干預司法作供 |publisher=《[[明報|明報]]》加西版 |date=2019-02-28 |accessdate=2019-12-09 |archive-date=2019-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204143221/http://www.mingpaocanada.com/VAN/htm/NEWS/20190228/vaa1h_r.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

另一方面，王州迪曾於2018年12月與[[加拿大樞密院|樞密院]]書記沃尼克（{{lang|en|Michael Wernick}}）電話通話，當中沃尼克稱杜魯多要求就SNC案作延期起訴。該段通話被王州迪秘密錄音，並於2019年3月29日公布<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/wilson-raybould-justice-committee-documents-audio-1.5076563 |title=PM wanted SNC-Lavalin deal 'one way or another', top bureaucrat told Wilson-Raybould in secretly recorded call |access-date=March 30, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330091143/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/wilson-raybould-justice-committee-documents-audio-1.5076563 |archive-date=March 30, 2019 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://nationalpost.com/news/politics/newsalert-justice-committee-releases-texts-recording-from-wilson-raybould?video_autoplay=true |title=SNC-Lavalin: Committee releases texts, secret recording of Wernick from Jody Wilson-Raybould |access-date=2019-12-09 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116021858/https://nationalpost.com/news/politics/newsalert-justice-committee-releases-texts-recording-from-wilson-raybould?video_autoplay=true |dead-url=no }}</ref>。王州迪同時向下議院司法委員會呈交一份40頁文件，當中包括該段對話的文本以及一系列電郵和短訊<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-47754185|title=Secret tape increases pressure on Trudeau in SNC-Lavalin affair|date=March 30, 2019|publisher=BBC|access-date=March 30, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330090930/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-47754185|archive-date=March 30, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://ourcommons.azureedge.net/data/Wilson-RaybouldJody-e.pdf|title=Hon. Jody Wilson-Raybould, MP – Submission to the House of Commons Standing Committee on Justice and Human Rights|first=Jody|last=Wilson-Raybould|date=March 26, 2019|access-date=March 30, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329202727/https://ourcommons.azureedge.net/data/Wilson-RaybouldJody-e.pdf|archive-date=March 29, 2019}}</ref>。王州迪秘密錄音招來多名自由黨黨團成員批評，而她亦承認做法不當，但她認為這屬特殊情況，需為通話留下證據而逼不得已<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/htm/News/20190330/taa1_r.htm |title=王州迪爆秘密錄音印證 遭高層威脅撤司法部長職 承認錄音「不適當」 稱因情況特殊 |publisher=《[[明報|明報]]》加東版 |date=2019-03-30 |accessdate=2019-12-09 |archive-date=2019-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603191921/http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/htm/News/20190330/taa1_r.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2019年4月2日，特鲁多宣布因對王州迪和[[費普真|費普真]]失去信任而將兩人逐出[[加拿大自由党|自由党]]党团<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/htm/News/20190403/tda1_r.htm |title=杜魯多指信任打破無法挽回 將王州迪費普真踢出議員團 王州迪稱講出真相無遺憾 |publisher=《[[明報|明報]]》加東版 |date=2019-04-03 |accessdate=2019-12-09 |archive-date=2019-11-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191103015514/http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/htm/News/20190403/tda1_r.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並被禁止代表自由黨參加[[2019年加拿大聯邦大選|2019年大選]]；他稱王州迪秘密錄音的行為「不合情理」<ref name=expel>{{cite news |last1=Harris |first1=Kathleen |title=Trudeau ejects Wilson-Raybould, Philpott from Liberal caucus |url=https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/liberals-wilson-raybould-philpott-caucus-1.5080880 |accessdate=April 2, 2019 |publisher=Canadian Broadcasting Corporation |date=April 2, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402180454/https://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/liberals-wilson-raybould-philpott-caucus-1.5080880 |archive-date=April 2, 2019 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=SNC-Lavalin affair: Trudeau expels 'whistleblower' MPs |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-47754193 |publisher=BBC |date=April 2, 2019 |access-date=April 3, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403011824/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-47754193 |archive-date=April 3, 2019 }}</ref>。此後王州迪在所屬選區的個人支持度超越自由黨，她亦決定以無黨籍身分在大選中爭取連任<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.thestar.com/vancouver/2019/04/05/exclusive-wilson-raybould-could-beat-vancouver-riding-rivals-by-nearly-double-digits-poll-suggests.html |title=Jody Wilson-Raybould could beat Vancouver riding rivals by nearly double digits, poll suggests |publisher=The Star Vancouver |date=2019-04-06 |accessdate=2019-12-09 |first=David P. |last=Ball |archive-date=2020-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200422215254/https://www.thestar.com/vancouver/2019/04/05/exclusive-wilson-raybould-could-beat-vancouver-riding-rivals-by-nearly-double-digits-poll-suggests.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/jody-wilson-raybould-has-the-lead-over-trudeaus-liberals/ |title=Jody Wilson-Raybould has the lead over Trudeau's Liberals |publisher=MacLean's |date=2019-06-03 |accessdate=2019-12-09 |first=Philippe J. |last=Fournier |archive-date=2019-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129004601/https://www.macleans.ca/politics/ottawa/jody-wilson-raybould-has-the-lead-over-trudeaus-liberals/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。最終她以32.6%得票率成功連任溫哥華固蘭湖選區議員，但好友費普真則落選<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.singtao.ca/3860619/2019-10-22/post-%e7%8e%8b%e5%b7%9e%e8%bf%aa%e7%8d%a8%e7%ab%8b%e5%8f%83%e9%81%b8%e5%a5%8f%e5%87%b1-%e5%85%ac%e5%ae%89%e8%b3%87%e6%ba%902%e9%83%a8%e9%95%b7%e6%95%97%e9%81%b8/ |title=王州迪獨立參選奏凱 公安資源2部長敗選 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》加西版 |date=2019-10-22 |accessdate=2019-12-09 }}</ref>。

2021年2月她投票支持由保守党议员[[庄文浩|庄文浩]]发起，认定中国对[[维吾尔族种族灭绝|维吾尔族种族灭绝]]的议案。她於同年7月表示因有感聯邦政壇「毒性且不具效率」而宣布不在[[2021年加拿大聯邦大選|來屆大選]]尋求連任議員<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.singtao.ca/5052044/2021-07-09/post-%e9%a6%96%e4%bd%8d%e5%8e%9f%e4%bd%8f%e6%b0%91%e5%8f%b8%e6%b3%95%e9%83%a8%e9%95%b7%e7%8e%8b%e5%b7%9e%e8%bf%aa-%e6%8c%87%e5%9c%8b%e6%9c%83%e3%80%8c%e6%83%a1%e6%af%92%e3%80%8d%e6%a3%84%e8%a7%92-2/ |title=首位原住民司法部長王州迪 指國會「惡毒」棄角逐下屆大選 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》加西版 |date=2021-07-09 |accessdate=2021-11-07 }}</ref>，並於同年9月出版回憶錄描述她任職內閣部長的經歷<ref>{{cite news |url= https://www.singtao.ca/5209144/2021-09-12/post-%e7%8e%8b%e5%b7%9e%e8%bf%aa%e6%96%b0%e6%9b%b8%e7%88%86%e6%96%99%e6%8c%87%e5%b0%8f%e6%9d%9c-%e7%9b%bc%e5%a5%b9%e5%9c%a8snc%e4%ba%8b%e4%bb%b6%e8%aa%aa%e8%ac%8a/ |title=王州迪新書爆料指小杜 盼她在SNC事件說謊 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》加西版 |date=2021-09-12 |accessdate=2021-11-07 }}</ref>。

